X-LIVEWHALE-SUMMARY:<p>\n  Whether you are leading a team today or prepar
 ing to lead one tomorrow\, this summit is for you. We welcome all <strong
 >current</strong> leaders\, <strong>applicants</strong> (RA\, NST\, NSPM\
 , GEM)\, and <strong>future</strong> trailblazers to come learn what it t
 akes to lead with impact.<br />\n  <br />\n  There will be food\, swag\, 
 and raffle prizes for participants.\n</p>
