 ng and practical career panel exploring the different pathways available 
 after law school: Taking the bar exam Pursuing an alternative licensure p
 athway Building a career without bar admission Hear from professionals wh
 o chose different routes and learn about the realities\, challenges\, and
  opportunities associated with each path.</p>
