X-LIVEWHALE-SUMMARY:<p>\n  Join us for a reception celebrating the Gender
  Studies Symposium art exhibit\, featuring work by community members from
  Lewis &amp\; Clark and beyond.<br />\n  <br />\n  Light refreshments wil
 l be provided.<br />\n  <br />\n  This year's exhibit includes a gallery 
 in the Watzek Library atrium and an online gallery.\n</p>\n<p>\n  Curated
  by L&amp\;C students <strong>Jamison Bane</strong> '27\, <strong>Finn Dw
 yer</strong> '28\, and <strong>Maria Martinez Decuir</strong> '27.\n</p>
