SUMMARY:2026 L&C Athletics Virtual Series: Wednesdays at 5
DESCRIPTION:From season previews and recruiting updates to stories of int
 ernational competition and professional careers in the NBA and beyond\, t
 hese sessions celebrate the journey of the student-athlete and the enduri
 ng strength of the L&amp\;C network. Whether you are a fan\, a former ath
 lete\, or a supporter of the program\, tune in to hear how we are buildin
 g a championship culture on the field\, in the classroom\, and throughout
  our community.  This series has two day/time slots: the third Wednesday 
 of every month at 5:00 PM Pacific Time and Thursdays at 12:00 Pacific Tim
 e - January 22nd and then the third Thursdays.Click to Register for one o
 r more of the Wednesday sessions (https://engage.lclark.edu/register/?id=
 fa8548f3-e4ce-433f-b0f9-b53e925dea22)Session Dates and Topics:January 21 
 5:00-6:00 PM PT: The Unified Front: From Local Leadership to the World St
 age  February 18 5:00-6:00 PM PT: Chasing Greatness: Recruitment\, Resear
 ch\, and the Road to Pro  March 18 5:00-6:00 PM PT: The Big League Path: 
 From Campus Internships to the NBA Front Office  April 15 5:00-6:00 PM PT
 : Stepping Up to the Plate: Leadership Lessons from L&amp\;C Athletics  M
 ay 20 5:00-6:00 PM PT: Leading from the Circle: Empowerment and Excellenc
 e in Sport  Additionally to learn more and register for one or more of th
 e sessions taking place on Thursdays at 12:00 Pacific Time\, visit this l
 ink (https://engage.lclark.edu/register/?id=3f52191c-dccb-40e3-ab98-a0794
 a499ce5).
X-ALT-DESC;FMTTYPE=text/html:<p>  From <strong>season previews</strong> a
 nd <strong>recruiting updates</strong> to <strong>stories of internationa
 l competition and professional careers in the NBA</strong> and beyond\, t
 hese sessions celebrate the journey of the student-athlete and the enduri
 ng strength of the L&amp\;C network. Whether you are a fan\, a former ath
 lete\, or a supporter of the program\, tune in to hear how we are buildin
 g a championship culture on the field\, in the classroom\, and throughout
  our community.</p><p>  This series has two day/time slots: the third Wed
 nesday of every month at 5:00 PM Pacific Time and Thursdays at 12:00 Paci
 fic Time - January 22nd and then the third Thursdays.<br /><a class="btn-
 small-style-1 btn-small-style-1 btn-small-style-1" href="https://engage.l
 clark.edu/register/?id=fa8548f3-e4ce-433f-b0f9-b53e925dea22" target="_bla
