 sions</a><br /><strong>Session Dates and Topics:</strong><br /><strong>Ja
 nuary 21 5:00-6:00 PM PT: The Unified Front:</strong> From Local Leadersh
 ip to the World Stage<strong><br />  February 18 5:00-6:00 PM PT: Chasing
  Greatness:</strong> Recruitment\, Research\, and the Road to Pro<strong>
