X-LIVEWHALE-SUMMARY:<p>\n  Join us for the <strong>2026 L&amp\;C Athletic
 s Virtual Series</strong>\, a dynamic collection of conversations that br
 ing the L&amp\;C community together from across the globe. This series of
 fers an insider's look at the <strong>"Pursuit of Excellence" within L&am
 p\;C Athletics\, featuring a unique 360-degree perspective from our dedic
 ated coaches\, inspiring current student-athletes\, and successful alumni
 .</strong>\n</p>
