 g a championship culture on the field\, in the classroom\, and throughout
  our community.This series has two day/time slots: the third Wednesday of
  every month at 5:00 PM Pacific Time and Thursdays at 12:00 Pacific Time 
 - January 22nd and then the third Thursdays thereafter.  This series take
 s place Thursday\, January 22 and thereafter the third Thursday of every 
