SUMMARY:L&C Alumni Lunch in Sacramento!
DESCRIPTION:Reconnect with your Lewis &amp\; Clark community right here i
 n the neighborhood. You're invited to a casual alumni lunch hosted by our
  very own Director of Alumni Relations\, Natasha Richmond '10.  Come for 
 the great food at Cafeteria 15L\, stay for the shared memories and new co
 nnections. Come and hear some updates on what's happening at L&amp\;C and
  get a sneak peek at our new River Otter (https://www.lclark.edu/about/ma
 scot/) swag. We'd love to see you there!When: Friday\, March 27 at 12 noo
 n    Where:Cafeteria 15L (https://www.cafeteria15l.com/)\, Sacramento    
 RSVP: Please RSVP HERE (https://engage.lclark.edu/register/?id=25d36a1e-f
 533-4a58-ae58-d86d1003b86a) by March 25th so we can save your seat!
