</picture></picture>Professor Berkson w
 as a presenter in Lewis &amp\; Clark's first Gender Studies Symposium. Fo
 r the gender studies minor\, she designed a course titled Gender and Aest
 hetic Expression\, which she continued to teach for many years.</em></p><
