 h Friday\, 7am to 7pm. Please see the Visiting Campus page (https://www.l
 clark.edu/visit/parking_and_transportation/visitor_parking/) for addition
 al details. For weekday events before 7pm\, visitors may purchase day pas
 ses online (https://lclark.t2hosted.com/Account/Portal) or via QR codes p
 osted in all major parking lots.
