 <span data-originalfontsize="14pt" data-originalcomputedfontsize="18.6666
 66">Join Kim StaffordŌĆöpoet\, retired professor at Lewis &amp\; Clark Co
 llege\, former Oregon Poet LaureateŌĆöto make travel more than seeing the
  sights. He will share how keeping a journal opens doors to deeper\, more
  meaningful connections to the places you</span></em>\n</p>\n<p>\n  &#160
