X-LIVEWHALE-SUMMARY:<p>\n  Join us for the <em><strong>4 at 5 Lecture Ser
 ies Featuring Pamplin Professor Emeritus Stephen Dow Beckham</strong></em
 >\, an exciting collection of four history lectures presented at 5:00 P.M
 . Pacific Time on the second Wednesday of each month. This series offers 
 an historical deep dive into people and events associated with a variety 
 of geographical regions with the aim of bringing our community together f
 rom across the nation to embark on a journey of discovery\, bridging the 
 past and present through the expert guidance of one of our institution's 
 most cherished academic luminaries.\n</p>
