X-LIVEWHALE-SUMMARY:<div id="lw_cal_event_detail_intro" class="lw_cal_eve
 nt_detail_block rich-text">\n  <h3 data-end="209" data-start="0">\n    Ou
 r Distinguished Business Law Graduate Award Reception will be held on Apr
 il 14 at 4:30 PM in downtown Portland as we honor our 2026 Distinguished 
 Business Law Graduate <a href="https://www.lclark.edu/live/profiles/14032
 -shawn-filippi-99" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Shawn Filippi '99</a>.<
 br />\n    <br />\n  </h3>\n  <p data-end="311" data-start="211">\n    We
  are also pleased to recognize the recipients of our 2026 Pro Bono Volunt
 eer of the Year awards:\n  </p>\n  <ul>\n    <li data-end="311" data-star
 t="211">\n      <strong><a href="https://www.ballardspahr.com/people/atto
 rneys/g/gutierrez-diego" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Diego Gutierrez '
 21\, Associate\, Ballard Spahr</a></strong>ŌĆō Low Income Tax Clinic Pro 
 Bono Volunteer of the Year\n    </li>\n    <li data-end="311" data-start=
 "211">\n      <strong data-end="403" data-start="384"><a href="https://ww
 w.ballardspahr.com/people/attorneys/y/yamaguchi-masa" target="_blank" rel
 ="noopener">Masa Yamaguchi '08\, Partner\, Ballard Spahr</a></strong> ŌĆō
  Small Business Legal Clinic Pro Bono Volunteer of the Year\n    </li>\n 
  </ul>\n  <p data-end="547" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="" dat
 a-start="445">\n    We look forward to celebrating these outstanding indi
 viduals and their contributions to our community!\n  </p>\n</div>\n<div i
 d="lw_cal_event_detail_description" class="lw_cal_event_detail_block rich
 -text">\n  <p data-start="445" data-end="547" data-is-last-node="" data-i
 s-only-node="">\n    Please note: This is a private event for invited gue
 sts only\n  </p>\n</div>
