X-LIVEWHALE-IMAGE:https://www.lclark.edu/live/image/gid/660/width/80/heig
 ht/80/crop/1/src_region/0\,0\,538\,532/110380_Screenshot_2025-10-27_12411
 7.rev.1761594099.png
X-LIVEWHALE-IMAGE-CAPTION:AHEC
X-LIVEWHALE-SUMMARY:<p>\n  ŌĆó Are you interested in exploring a career i
 n healthcare?<br />\n  ŌĆó Want to talk to someone who has been through t
 he process?<br />\n  <br />\n  Oregon <span class="il">AHEC</span> is hos
 ting a monthly virtual panel series for undergrad students and high schoo
 l students interested in careers in healthcare. The panels are composed o
 f a rotating mix of <span class="il">AHEC</span> Scholars and other gradu
 ate level students\, with a facilitator keeping the conversation flowing.
  These are informal discussions and a fun\, informative way to learn abou
 t what different careers and pathways can look like\, and tips to navigat
 e the path.<br />\n  <br />\n  <a href="https://ohsu.ca1.qualtrics.com/jf
 e/form/SV_6ffB7Sk7vISodgi" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Register here</
 a>!<br />\n  <br />\n  For more information\, contact Kate Hubbard at <a 
 href="mailto:hubbarka@ohsu.edu">hubbarka@ohsu.edu</a>. If you need an acc
 ommodation to participate in this event please contact <a href="mailto:ah
 ec@ohsu.edu">ahec@ohsu.edu</a> at least five business days prior to the e
 vent.\n</p>
END:VEVENT
