X-LIVEWHALE-IMAGE:https://www.lclark.edu/live/image/gid/485/width/80/heig
 ht/80/crop/1/src_region/0\,0\,500\,500/106854_CSCCI_Logo.rev.1737656814.p
 ng
X-LIVEWHALE-IMAGE-CAPTION:cscci logo
X-LIVEWHALE-CONTACT-INFO:<p>\n  Questions? Contact <a href="mailto:leadse
 rve@lclark.edu">leadserve@lclark.edu</a>&#160\;\n</p>
X-LIVEWHALE-SUMMARY:<p>\n  Interested in a mentorship opportunity? Sign u
 p to volunteer with the Center for Social Change as we welcome a group of
  3rd graders and future scholars from Alder Elementary School. Lead a cam
 pus tour and/or host an interactive activity to give a students a glimpse
  of college life. BIPOC and/or Spanish speaking students encouraged to si
 gn up! Multiple shifts will be available for this event. There is some fl
 exibility around shift timing and roles available. The general time commi
 tment is expected to be around 2 hours. Please note that there will be a 
 30-minute volunteer training the week of the event.<br />\n  <br />\n  Sh
 ift 1: 9:40am-11:30am<br />\n  Shift 2: 11:20am-1:00pm<br />\n  <br />\n 
  <strong>Choose one of two volunteer roles for this event:</strong><br />
 \n  <br />\n  <strong>Tour Leader:</strong> Show students around campus a
 nd take them to activity areas for a scavenger hunt. Share your education
 al journey\, educate the students on the history of Lewis &amp\; Clark\, 
 and answer general questions from the kids.<br />\n  <strong>Activity Lea
