 ists: Madeleine Tran\, soprano\; Lisa Neher\, mezzo-soprano\; Brandon Mic
 hael\, tenor\; and Nicolas Vilches '26\, baritone\, with Katherine FitzGi
 bbon\, conductor.  Lewis &amp\; Clark's featured ensembles include Cappel
 la Nova and Community Chorale (Katherine FitzGibbon\, director)\, Voces A
 uream (John Cox\, director)\, and the Lewis &amp\; Clark Orchestra (Lance
  Inouye\, director).Tickets are on sale now! (https://app.arts-people.com
 /index.php?ticketing=lccmd) This performance will be live streamed here. 
 (https://vimeo.com/event/4079258)  &#160\;Parking at Lewis &amp\; Clark -
