X-LIVEWHALE-SUMMARY:<p>\n  Join us for the <em><strong>4 at 5 Lecture Ser
 ies Featuring Pamplin Professor Emeritus Stephen Dow Beckham</strong></em
 >\, an exciting collection of four history lectures presented at 5:00 P.M
 . the second Wednesday of each month. This series offers an historical de
 ep dive into people and events associated with a variety of geographical 
 regions with the aim of bringing our community together from across the n
 ation to embark on a journey of discovery\, bridging the past and present
  through the expert guidance of one of our institution's most cherished a
 cademic luminaries.\n</p>
