LOCATION:McAfee
GEO:45.4479004644199;-122.669466498642
SUMMARY:McAfee is Turning 25: Come for the Tour\, Stay for the Cake!
DESCRIPTION:The McAfee Building: From Temporary to Timeless  McAfee arriv
 ed on campus in 2001 as a prefabricated single-story office building with
  a basement storeroom. It was never meant to be a permanent fixture on ca
 mpus\, but over the years\, a funny thing happened: we added a room here\
 , a renovation there\, and somewhere between the first coat of paint and 
 constructing several additional offices\, the building put down permanent
  roots.  McAfee's offices now include: Advancement (https://college.lclar
 k.edu/giving/contact_us/)\, Communications (https://www.lclark.edu/office
 s/communications/staff/)\, Equity and Inclusion (https://www.lclark.edu/a
 bout/equity-and-inclusion/staff/)\, Human Resources (https://www.lclark.e
 du/offices/human_resources/staff/)\, and the Mailroom (https://www.lclark
 .edu/offices/mail_services/).  Please join us as we celebrate this quarte
 r century anniversaryŌĆöacknowledging the staying power of a place that r
 efused to be temporary. It turns out that when you fill a space with enou
 gh heart\, history\, and coffee spills\, it becomes impossible to move.&#
 160\;
X-ALT-DESC;FMTTYPE=text/html:<h4>  The McAfee Building: From Temporary to
  Timeless</h4><p>  McAfee arrived on campus in 2001 as a prefabricated si
 ngle-story office building with a basement storeroom. It was never meant 
 to be a permanent fixture on campus\, but over the years\, a funny thing 
 happened: we added a room here\, a renovation there\, and somewhere betwe
 en the first coat of paint and constructing several additional offices\, 
 the building put down permanent roots.</p><p>  McAfee's offices now inclu
 de: <a href="https://college.lclark.edu/giving/contact_us/">Advancement</
 a>\, <a href="https://www.lclark.edu/offices/communications/staff/">Commu
 nications</a>\, <a href="https://www.lclark.edu/about/equity-and-inclusio
 n/staff/">Equity and Inclusion</a>\, <a href="https://www.lclark.edu/offi
 ces/human_resources/staff/">Human Resources</a>\, and the <a href="https:
 //www.lclark.edu/offices/mail_services/">Mailroom</a>.</p><p>  Please joi
 n us as we celebrate this quarter century anniversaryŌĆöacknowledging the
  staying power of a place that refused to be temporary. It turns out that
  when you fill a space with enough heart\, history\, and coffee spills\, 
 it becomes impossible to move.&#160\;</p>
