 rks at her Private Practice Cloudburst Counseling and specializes in work
 ing with young adults and teens with eating disorders\, body image distre
 ss\, and anxiety. She received her Eating Disorder Certification from Lew
 is and Clark\, where she completed her Master's degree\, and has previous
 ly worked in residential and outpatient eating disorder care. Abby is a b
 oard member of the Columbia River Eating Disorder Network and is passiona
 te about eating disorder education for therapists. Abby is committed to f
 at liberation\, body neutrality\, and operates from a Health at Every Siz
 e lens.</p><div id="lw_widget_470b39ba" class="lw_widget lw_widget_type_b
