 e="line-height: 1.5\;"><strong>Instructor:</strong> Krystal Marcinkiewicz
 \, MA\, LPC\, LMHC</p><p style="line-height: 1.5\;"><strong>Current Stude
 nts and Certificate Candidates:</strong> CECP 837-2\, 1 semester hour of 
 Graduate Continuing Education credit\, $385.&#160\;</p><p style="line-hei
